name: Beastmaster Strikeforce - Nueve Knight
description: A champion royal guard that was betrayed by his own kingdom has sought refuge with the strikeforce. Honor and sacrifice are his calling cards loyal to almost a fault. He has sworn his allegiance to the team in order to fight back against anyone that breaks his code of honor and seeks vengeance for the innocent. Has the ability to fly at supersonic speed and his sword is made from unbreakable other worldly material that is yet to be identified. His sword has the ability to interact with ancient magic.
